<h2 style="color:#18181b; font-size:22px; font-weight:700; margin:0 0 16px;">Payment failed — action required.</h2>

<p style="color:#52525b; font-size:15px; margin:0 0 16px;">
  Hey <%= @user.first_name.presence || @user.username %> —
</p>

<p style="color:#52525b; font-size:15px; margin:0 0 16px;">
  We weren't able to process your payment for Train Like Dubi. This can happen if your card has expired, was declined, or has insufficient funds.
</p>

<div style="background-color:#fef2f2; border:1px solid #fecaca; border-radius:8px; padding:16px 20px; margin:0 0 24px;">
  <p style="color:#991b1b; font-size:14px; font-weight:600; margin:0 0 4px;">Payment could not be processed</p>
  <p style="color:#991b1b; font-size:14px; margin:0;">
    Please update your billing information to keep your access.
  </p>
</div>

<p style="color:#52525b; font-size:15px; margin:0 0 24px;">
  Your access will remain active for a short grace period while we retry. Update your payment method now to avoid any interruption.
</p>

<p style="text-align:center; margin:0 0 28px;">
  <%= link_to "Update Payment Method",
      root_url,
      style: "display:inline-block; padding:14px 32px; background-color:#dc2626; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:8px; font-weight:700; font-size:15px;" %>
</p>

<hr style="border:none; border-top:1px solid #e4e4e7; margin:0 0 20px;">

<p style="color:#71717a; font-size:13px; margin:0;">
  Need help? Reply to this email or reach us at
  <a href="mailto:support@trainlikedubi.com" style="color:#ef4444; text-decoration:none;">support@trainlikedubi.com</a>.
</p>
